{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/discove__explore_survive_eng.png?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/gif_road_616.gif?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into Wasteland Punk \u2014 the ultimate RPG of survival in a world shattered by catastrophe! Face a gripping story full of twists, fierce enemies, and intense turn-based combat. Unleash your tactical brilliance with weapons forged or scavenged from the ruins of civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/gif_battle_616.gif?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world torn apart by solar flares, essentials like clean water and food are luxuries worth killing for. Scavenge the remnants of a fallen civilization, where every corner hides danger and secrets. Battle ruthless factions and secretive organizations fighting for dominance, unleashing monsters and covert operations from the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/city_building_and_craft_eng.png?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/city_616.gif?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead your squad of mercenaries through a vast open world in your armored pickup. Take on daring missions, build your reputation, and gather resources to craft powerful weapons and develop a thriving base. Decide who joins your team and who\u2019s left to perish in the wasteland\u2019s scorched sands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/open_world_exploration_eng.png?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/gif_road_616.gif?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore each location packed with enemies and clues to dark secrets. Question settlers, raid bandit camps, and uncover surprises. Be ready for battle at all times! Use fire, poison, electricity, and more to exploit your enemies\u2019 weaknesses. Combine unique abilities, wield powerful weapons, and upgrade your squad with the classic RPG system.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/tactical_combats_and_deep_role_playing_system_eng.png?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/gif_battle_3_616.gif?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Master the art of strategy! Set traps, distract foes, and adapt your tactics. Collect resources, enhance your base, and create hundreds of weapons and gear. Equip swords, rifles, rocket launchers, and more with deadly modifiers. Withstand sniper shots and turn the tide of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/extras/car.gif?t=1734091327\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you conquer Wasteland Punk or fall to the wasteland\u2019s embrace? Add the game to your wishlist and prepare for the ultimate post-apocalyptic adventure!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734091327","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2971970/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1734091327","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c